

MIME access-type name: news-message-ID

Required parameters:
	NAME, containing the message ID identifying the news article
	that constitutes the body

Optional parameters:
	SITE, suggesting a host where the body might be found using NNTP
	if it is not found (by host-specific means) locally

Published specification:
	RFCs 822 (message IDs), 1036 (application to news), 977 (NNTP)

Person & email address to contact for further
information:
	Henry Spencer
	henry@zoo.toronto.edu

                                         Henry Spencer at U of Toronto Zoology
                                          henry@zoo.toronto.edu   utzoo!henry

